  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Trimming"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 38,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "points = np.array(points)\n",
    "maxs = points.max(axis=0)\n",
    "mins = points.min(axis=0)\n",
    "xr = maxs[0] - mins[0]\n",
    "yr = maxs[1] - mins[1]\n",
    "buff = 0.05\n",
    "r = max(yr, xr) * buff\n",
    "minx = mins[0] - r\n",
    "miny = mins[1] - r\n",
    "maxx = maxs[0] + r\n",
    "maxy = maxs[1] + r"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 39,
   "metadata": {
    "scrolled": true
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 432x288 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {
      "needs_background": "light"
     },
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "fig, ax = plt.subplots()\n",
    "regions_df.plot(ax=ax, edgecolor=\"black\", facecolor=\"blue\", alpha=0.2)\n",
    "points_df.plot(ax=ax, color=\"red\")\n",
    "plt.xlim(minx, maxx)\n",
    "plt.ylim(miny, maxy)\n",
    "plt.title(\"buffer: %f, n: %d\" % (r, n_points))\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
